 🏥 Medical Appointment Scheduling System

A Java-based console application that allows users to manage doctor-patient appointments efficiently.

---

📌 Features

- 👨‍⚕ Add doctors with specialties
- 👤 Register patients with age and contact info
- 📅 Book appointments with date and time
- 🗓 View all scheduled appointments
- ✅ Simple and user-friendly CLI

---

 🧑‍💻 Technologies Used

- Java (JDK 8+)
- Java Collections (ArrayList)
- Java Time API (LocalDateTime)
- Object-Oriented Programming

---

🚀 Getting Started

 ✅ Prerequisites
- Java JDK installed (8 or above)
- Any IDE (IntelliJ, Eclipse) or CLI support

🔧 Compile & Run

```bash
javac -d out src/model/.java src/system/.java src/Main.java
java -cp out Main
